  "intro_paragraph": "Derived from the Spanish word for chickpeas, Ciceritos means little chickpeas in Ladino. This comforting Sephardic stew features tender legumes simmered in a golden turmeric broth. Naturally plant-based, it relies on a savory base of fried onions and celery to deliver deep flavor without any meat products.",
